p: I H.G. Thornton upon oath do say, that I am the person named written to whose said writ was issued to be served one Ah Chow that I delivered said writ to him on the 23d day of January 1874 ( the on the 21st day of Jany 1874) at the city of Seattle in said Territory
Subscribed and Sworn to before me this 23d day of Jan 1874
At the request and at the writ of the named petitioners, I hereby authorize H.G. Thorton to return the within warrant
